{"type":"text","timestamp":1775867716402,"sessionID":"ses_28609c010ffedqfVqkP20ULmPO","part":{"id":"prt_d79f6bc7d001Hn4Z71nBiuPg57","messageID":"msg_d79f6a8b0001TEpYxHfZ6nZbVK","sessionID":"ses_28609c010ffedqfVqkP20ULmPO","type":"text","text":"## AR-021 — CLI build 命令 Archive\n\n### Completed\n\n**CLI Interface (`cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/main.py:129-177`):**\n- `build` Typer subcommand with all required flags: `--workspace/-f`, `--proxy/-p`, `--cloud-provider`, `--output`, `--verbose`\n- Default workspace resolution to current directory\n- Rich-formatted success output showing image name, ID, and size\n- Error handling with traceback display in verbose mode\n\n**BuildRuntime (`cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py`):**\n- Local Docker build flow via `DockerService`\n- Cloud build stub (returns placeholder result)\n- Version increment logic with rollback on failure (patch, pre-release, fallback handling)\n- Build prerequisites validation (Dockerfile existence, Docker availability)\n- Proxy support via build args\n- Metadata update after successful build\n\n**DockerService (`cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py`):**\n- Docker availability check\n- Image build with build args (proxy support)\n- Human-readable image size formatting\n- Image registry push with authentication\n- Image tagging and removal\n\n**Tests (`cmd/cli/tests/test_build_command.py`):**\n- 12 test cases covering: help output, success path, proxy/cloud/output/verbose options, error handling (missing Dockerfile, runtime errors), default workspace, integration flow\n\n---\n\n### Deferred\n\n**Cloud Build (REQ-021.6):**\n- `_build_cloud()` returns stub result; no actual Huawei Cloud Container Registry API integration\n- Cloud build status polling and timeout handling not implemented\n- Cloud provider credential validation not implemented\n\n**Version Increment (REQ-021.5):**\n- Only patch version increment implemented\n- Minor/major version bump flags not exposed in CLI\n- Version revert tested but relies on exception propagation\n\n**Proxy Configuration (REQ-021.9):**\n- Proxy passed as Docker build arg only\n- No pip `--proxy` flag integration for Python dependencies\n- No Maven proxy settings.xml integration for Java\n\n**Build Output (REQ-021.8):**\n- Missing \"Build time\" in success output\n- No \"next step guidance\" suggesting `agentcube publish`\n- Build time not calculated/formatted\n\n**Validation (REQ-021.7):**\n- Image name sanitization for Docker naming rules not implemented\n\n**Open Questions (from spec):**\n- `--tag` override for custom image tags\n- Multi-platform builds (`--platform`)\n- Build cache options (`--no-cache`, `--cache-from`)","time":{"start":1775867716399,"end":1775867716399}}}
